## Description {#details}

A wrapper around <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/analysisusage">AnalysisUsage</a> for the purpose of uniqueing.

The wrapper is used to avoid needing to make <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/analysisusage">AnalysisUsage</a> itself a folding set node.
